Vital Point to Capture?(8)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par Black has an eye on the right side.
\par So White has to destroy the eye on the left side.
\par
\par If White finds the first move, the follow up comes naturally.
\par
\par
\par }
