Dia. 01 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par It wasn't a complicated problem, was it?
\par White 1 was the \cf1\b first move\cf0\b0 .
\par After Black 2, White plays at 3 and 5 so Black eye becomes a false eye on the left.
\par
\par }
