Dia. 02 In Actual Game?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par If White is not careful enough, it is common to play a move like White 1.
\par Black takes at 2 and lives.
\par
\par It was a big mistake from White to play like this in the actual game.
\par He should have played just like it was shown in \b Dia. 01\b0 .
\par
\par
\par }
