Dia. 04 Nice Attack
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White's exchange with the cut at 1 for Black 2 is a \cf1\b nice attack\cf0\b0 . It doesn't give a chance for Black to resist.
\par
\par After that White destroys the eye with 3, just as we learned in \b Dia. 01\b0 .
\par
\par }
